snippet.title: Sniper Killer - Official Launch Trailer | The Indie Horror Showcase 2024
snippet.description:
Watch the launch trailer for Sniper Killer, an indie action sniper game developed by Black Eyed Priest and Henry Hoare. Traverse rooftops and remain undetected to complete sniper kills to then switch roles as the detective to question the very same crime. Sniper Killer is available now for PC.

#SniperKiller #Gaming #IndieHorrorShowcase2024
